text:
EXO KINGS AND LEGENDS OF K-POP 
FOREVER ETERNA–A FACT THAT HAS 
NO LONGER NEEDS ANYONE'S APPROVAL.
POPULARITY AND LEGNDARITY ARE 
DIFFERENT CONCEPTS. Popularity is 
there today, tomorrow it is gone, and

EXO songs released in 2012 in their 
debut album are relevant to this day. 
EVERY EXO ALBUM IS A VISION OF ART 
THAT YOU CAN LISTEN TO ENDLESSLY. 
EXO MUSIC IS TIMELESS. EXO ARE 
RELEVANT EVEN AFTER 11 YEARS 
OF CAREER.

author: @liza_pet
text: IT's been 11 YEARS NOW, BUT EXO'S VOCALS ARE STILL THE BEST AND MOST SOULFUL I've ever heard IN THE ENTIRE K-POP INDUSTRY. And no, it's not an exaggeration or bias, it's THE PURE TRUTH.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Once again, I am convinced that EXO is the biggest diamond, not only in the entire history 
of sm, but in the entire history of the K-POP industry. It's been 11 years, but I haven't seen 
a better band, especially with regard to vocals.

author: @liza_pet
text: 11 years have passed, but I have said and will say EXO is a real diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. Almost everything that is being done now is purely American POP songs literally licked from the West. EXO are one of the very few remaining who personify and preserve the real K-POP while continuing to keep up with the times. EXO music is beyond time and language barriers, so it was, is and will be.

author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is a diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. I sincerely apologize, but the visual effects of EXO are too powerful, as soon as they appear on the stage, they capture you with their dazzle, not letting you go until the very end. It's been a whole 11 years, but they simply have no equal in live performances.

author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is my very first and only favorite band in the entire industry. It doesn't matter how many more years pass, EXO were, are and will be Kings of K-POP, Kings of Vocals, Legends and Discoverers of the 3rd generation. EXO, even after 11 years of career, are the most popular, sought-after and highly paid SM group. Yes, because they are their best band in the history of the company. EXO is the only band with such a variety of high-quality music, choreography and visual effects.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Each song of each EXO album is 
a separate masterpiece unlike the 
previous one and absolutely every 
time they surpass themselves.

text:
IN ADDITION TO THE FACT THAT EXO HAS LONG OUTGROWN SM, THEY HAVE LONG PROVED THEIR TALENT TO EVERYONE

ENTIRE MUSIC INDUSTRY.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Прошло 11 лет но я говорила и буду говорить EXO–самый настоящий бриллиант не только SM а всей K-POP индустрии. Практически всё что сейчас делают это чисто американский POP песни в буквальном смысле слизанные 
с запада. EXO одни из очень немногих оставшихся кто олицетворяет и сохраняет настоящий K-POP при этом продолжая идти в ногу со временем. Музыка EXO вне времени и языковых барьеров так было есть и будет.
